As in GuideScan, we define the gRNA specificity score as an aggregate of the cutting frequency determination (CFD) scores [13] across all off-targets:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
