FASTQ files were processed and aligned to the reference sgRNA library file, and log2 fold change value for each sgRNA was calculated using MAGeCK v0.5.9.2 [31]. Only the gRNAs with control read count > 100 were used in subsequent analysis. For analysis of gRNAs targeting essential genes, average LFC per gene was calculated across all gRNAs used in the screen for that gene, and only the genes with such average below \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
